episodes.title: “I Was Raised In a Cult… and Taken Into Care at 14” | Part 3
episodes.description:
In part 3 of The Unspoken Truth, we hear from Wealth who survived a childhood shaped by belief systems she did not choose. Introduced to a cult by her own father, her life took a devastating turn, and by the age of 14, she was taken into care.

This conversation is not about exposing a cult for shock value. It’s about the lasting impact of psychological control, growing up without safety, and the difficult journey of rebuilding identity after leaving everything you were taught to believe.

She opens up about trust, survival, and what it truly means to find your voice after years of silence.

Raw. Honest.
This is The Unspoken Truth.
